http://www.campchef.com/smokers-grills/wood-pellets/herb-pellets-mediterranean-blend.html

Camp Chef herb pellets are simply 100% herbs. No oils, chemicals or binders added. Just herbs. This will add a pure flavor to your favorite foods. Because of the high concentrate in flavors these pellets are intended to be mixed with other hardwood pellets for best results. Suggested use is 5lbs of hardwood pellets to every 1lb of herb pellets or less depending on your personal preference.
